rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description:
A virtual property that relates a television actor to information about the actor's roles as a guest character on a television program.  Note that this virtual property should be redefined as follows: 

construct
{
?tv.actor mso:tv.actor.guest_roles ?guest_roles.
}
where
{
?guest_roles mso:tv.appearance.agent ?tv.actor.
?guest_roles mso:tv.guest_role.character ?character.
?tv.actor mso:type.object.type mso:tv.actor.
}

A virtual property that relates a television actor to information about the actor's role as a regular character on a television program.  Note that this virtual property should be redefined as follows:  

construct
    {
      ?tv.actor mso:tv.actor.starring_roles ?starring_roles.
    }
    where
    {
      ?starring_roles mso:tv.appearance.agent ?tv.actor.
      ?starring_roles mso:tv.regular_tv_appearance.character ?character.
      ?tv.actor mso:type.object.type mso:tv.actor.
    }

A virtual property that links a television personality to information about television programs where he or she appears regularly as himself/herself.  Note that this virtual property should be redefined as follows:

construct
{
?tv.personality mso:tv.personality.tv_regular_appearances ?tv_regular_appearances.
}
where
{
?tv_regular_appearances mso:type.object.type mso:tv.regular_personal_appearance.
?tv_regular_appearances mso:tv.appearance.agent ?tv.personality.
}
